page
在输出和索引页面之前调用。
页面对象



页对象
{
    // Parser named
    "type": "markdown",

    // File Path relative to book root
    "path": "page.md",

    // Absolute file path
    "rawpath": "/usr/...",

    // Title of the page in the SUMMARY
